snippet.title: Judge Rules in Favor of Amber Heard, Is Johnny Depp's Career Over | InformOverload
snippet.description:
Judge Rules in Favor of Amber Heard, Is Johnny Depp's Career Over | InformOverload
Subscribe To InformOverload: http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA
Recent Uploads: https://bit.ly/3mNYRdU

By now you’ve likely heard that Johnny Depp lost his legal battle against the tabloid The Sun, who in a 2018 article referred to him as a wife beater. A High Court judge ruled that the claims are substantially true, leading to Depp’s libel suit against The Sun to unfortunately be ruled in favor of the publication. We’ve been covering the Johnny and Amber story for quite some time now, and although the two of them are still in a back and forth, Johnny's legal team has filed to appeal the ruling in regards to the libel case. The judge also seemed to think some of Johnny’s claims we’re a little far-fetched, and for whatever reason, is willing to accept everything Amber says as the truth, but has a hard time believing Johnny’s side of the story.
